        fileName: _jsxFileName,
        lineNumber: 105,
        columnNumber: 19
      }
    }), "I recall those early morning evangelism trips for the drama, Escape. YouI can hear bro Okikiolu\u2019s voice shouting Escape on those loud speakers as early as 5am. And this reminds me of Sis Enitan of blessed memory. Those were not any ordinary drama. SCM received a lift spiritually and numerically due to this event. And I\u2019m glad the culture is now an SCM tradition. Kudos to all drama group members of that year. That event made us to be more spiritually ready and vigilant.", /*#__PURE__*/React.createElement("br", {
      __self: this,
