    }), "Mine may not be as spectacular as a few as I have been privileged to read, sovour and relish with some deep sense of nostalgia on this platform, but I\u2019d start from somewhere. I\u2019d like to deeply express my profound appreciation to our ever amiable Sister Ronke and Bro Bisi (who actually contacted me and brought me on this platform). I got the admission into UI Computer Science Dept. during the 1991/92 academic session.  I recall joining SCM sometime in 1992. It was Sister Seyi Olufiade (my class/course mate) that invited me.", /*#__PURE__*/React.createElement("br", {
