    }), "Before then I had a few stints with Deeper Life and NFCS (Nigeria Fellowship of Catholic Students). During my 100level I had about 11 or 13 roommates in Zik Hall (where I stayed throughout my stay in UI) and they were 97% Deeper Lifers so after a bit of consistent persuasions I followed them to fellowship a few times but I couldn\u2019t just fit in. However, prior to my visits to deeper life campus fellowship UI, I was born and raised in the Catholic church. I was the most senior mass server at my local church before I got into UI. Well entrenched in catholicism. I grew up as a devout Catholic obeying the 10 commandments with godly piety.", /*#__PURE__*/React.createElement("br", {
