    }), "The story of my life as a Christian and SCMer actually began in university of Ibadan in 1987. Not really sure of the date now. I remembered when I wrote my jamb I became very apprehensive of the result because I was not able to complete the maths exam. I became troubled not sure if I would spend more years of post wasc at home having already wasted five years at home. One night I was praying and asking God to intervene concerning the outcome of the result exam, a thought came to me \u201Cwhy don\u2019t you vow to God you will Serve Him wholeheartedly when you get admitted to UI\u201D.", /*#__PURE__*/React.createElement("br", {
