n, the .moment one fellowship ends you began to anticipate another one. No complain of spending too much time even if the fellowship stop by 1am. However it was a bitter pill to our Senior brethrens in the town We all love it, prophecy that followed deep praise and worship was a great consolation to our heart and we were never afraid. It was a normal thing to see people getting healed and delivered from demonic oppression.I remembered  the fear I broght to school following the mysterious demise of my father which almost paralysed me fizzled out in His presence and I was giving a heart of a lion. I later join organising subgroup because then the brother used to carry the Instruments on their head to Philistine road In bro Bola\u2019sroom. He was the fellowship keyboardist then. So I joined this group to relieve this wonderful brother who was doing the work as if he was receiving salary from it. Sometimes we may not get to our room until 1:30-200am. But we were doing it wholeheartedly without complain. Mine was to try to pay my vow for my admission\u2026serve me wholeheartedly was the bargain. God has taken me above all barriers of advancing in my academic carrier and being the first to break such a record among my brothers and siblings  of over twenty of us. No wonder the devil took my father thinking there won\u2019t be any forging ahead after the demise of my father. But God is faithful,\u2026 when your father and mother forsake you the Lord will take you up. And He was truthful to His word. My five years in ui witnessed this faithfulness to His word. His provision was always there to meet any need at anytime anyhow. Glory be to His name!!!", /*#__PURE__*/React.createElement("br", {
      __self: this,
      __source: {
        fileName: _jsxFileName,
        lineNumber: 436,
        columnNumber: 15
      }
    }), "Permit me to say that I had some challenges of doctrinal differences from Deeper life school fellowship. As I was very na\xEFve young convert eager to grow . I attended one of their fellowship and then hell was let loose. They kept bombarding me bringing many trivial issues ranging from hair btaiding , perming, shirt wearing of our sisters and that I need to come out from among them. They almost succeeded in winning me so I starts following them. But then SCM brethren were not taking no for an answer. The fish they\u2019d caught must not be let go like that\u2026is a sacrilege to allow that.", /*#__PURE__*/React.createElement("br", {
