        columnNumber: 15
      }
    }), "About the time of rounding up our five years program In Animal Science the Spirit of the Lord began to move. It was moving me in another crucial direction of life. Really I wasn\u2019t prepare for this\u2026but the one that I\u2019ve entrusted my life into his care said it\u2019s time to do this. Mind you I broke up with every unholy alliances of both men and women girl or boy  so as to please my Master and Lover Jesus. I didn\u2019t hold anything back from Him. So it was time for Him to lead me to fulfil this scripture \u201C \u2026he that finds a wife find a good thing and obtains favour from the lord\u2026..", /*#__PURE__*/React.createElement("br", {
